item.title: About
item.description:
I am a PhD student at the University of Minnesota. In May 2015, I received my B.S. and B.A. from the University of St. Thomas, St. Paul. I majored in statistics, mathematics, and actuarial science and minored in renaissance. Education Ph.D. Student, School of Statistics, University of Minnesota, 2015 - Present. B.S., B.A., Statistics, Mathematics, Actuarial Science, University of St. Thomas Actuarial Science, Heriot-Watt University, Scotland, 2014.
Resume. CV.
